snippet.title: Zelda: Ocarina of Time Completely Remade in Super Mario 64
snippet.description:
Super Mario 64 modder Kaze Emanuar has done the seemingly impossible by inserting the Mushroom Kingdom into Hyrule, which is now built from the ground up to be completed using Mario. Make sure to subscribe to Kaze on his YouTube channel for even more amazing rom hacks for the game.

https://www.youtube.com/c/KazeEmanuar

Subscribe to IGN for more!
